Class ToolView

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • org.pvg.plasmagraph.views.ToolView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class ToolView
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    View for the optional tools modification pane. Defines the visual organization of a JPanel embedded into MainView's JTabbedPane, and communicates changes done to the View to the Model via the Controller's Listeners.
    Author:
    Plasma Visualization Group
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
